 just 1 tablet a day, you can top up your body's natural levels of both vitamin C and zinc. One bottle gives you 180 tablets for a long-lasting 6-month supply.",{"children":"With 1000mg of vitamin C and 10mg of zinc per serving, our high strength Vitamin C and Zinc Tablets are made for you! With just 1 tablet a day, you can top up your body's natural levels of both vitamin C and zinc. One bottle gives you 180 tablets for a long-lasting 6-month supply."}],["$","p","They are also vegan, free from GMOs and contain no magnesium stearate, giving you only the goodness of premium-grade ingredients. Try them today and experience the difference in your well-being!",{"children":"They are also vegan, free from GMOs and contain no magnesium stearate, giving you only the goodness of premium-grade ingredients. Try them today and experience the difference in your well-being!"}]]]]}]
